report from the Evaluation Committee which had visited the Hong
Kong Special Administrative Region earlier this year, said Chan.
</P>
<P>
"He assured me that the voting on who will win the bid for the
2006 Asian Games will be done on a fair basis, and he encouraged
us to keep up with our lobbying efforts - which of course we will
do," Chan said. 
