<HEADLINE> Chinese Defense Minister Meets Italian Guests </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 15 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Defense Minister Chi
Haotian met here today with Alberto Zlgnani, Italian defense
secretary-general, and his party.
</P>
<P>
