</P>
<P>
Meeting with reporters in New York Thursday before his talks
with U.S. Secretary of State Madeleine Albright, who briefed him on
the bilateral talks in Washington between U.S. officials and
Palestinian negotiators, Ben-Ami said that the work should now
concentrate on "all the issues".
</P>
<P>
He said it should not appear as if the resolution of the
Jerusalem issue finalizes an agreement. 
</P>
