the Party and the State; reflecting the people's legitimate
aspirations; and actively participating in the country's struggle
against corruption, red tape and other social evils.
</P>
<P>
VNA has its headquarters in Hanoi, two presentative offices in
Ho Chi Minh City and the central city of Da Nang, 61 bureaux
across the country, and 23 offices across Asia, Europe, Africa,
American and Australia. 
